{"word":"G2745 - καύχημα - kaúchēma - kow'-khay-mah - Boasting","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καύχημα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kaúchēma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kow'-khay-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Boasting"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"மேன்மை, புகழ்ச்சி, மகிழ்ச்சி - பால்வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. that of which one glories or can glory, matter or ground of glorying"},{"paragraph":"2. a glorying, boasting"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2744 - καυχάομαι - kaucháomai - kow-khah'-om-ahee/2744\">G2744</a>; a <i>boast</i> (properly the objective; by implication the act) in a good or bad sense: - boasting, (whereof) to glory (of), glorying, rejoice (-ing)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2620 - κατακαυχάομαι - katakaucháomai - kat-ak-ow-khah'-om-ahee/2620\">G2620</a>, <a href=\"#/G2744 - καυχάομαι - kaucháomai - kow-khah'-om-ahee/2744\">G2744</a>, <a href=\"#/G2745 - καύχημα - kaúchēma - kow'-khay-mah/2745\">G2745</a>, <a href=\"#/G2746 - καύχησις - kaúchēsis - kow'-khay-sis/2746\">G2746</a>"}]}